{
  "stem": "1292.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when I got my good result from school-- I [LAUGHS] remember I tried to look a bit more grown-up I was 17.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember putting on my auntie's outfit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I did think, I'll just try to go there and ask for the owner to have a word with him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I come there, it wasn't easy, because they was-- they did have their offices, and it wasn't easy to speak to them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But one of the-- office people came and asked me, 'Can I help you?' And I said, 'I would like to speak to Mr.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Alexandrovicz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, 'Well, what it is about?' And I said, 'Well, should I tell you I'm trying to get a job here?' And in this instance, I remember Mr.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Alexandrovicz came out of the office.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this man who worked there-- what was his name?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Can't remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He laughed, and he laughed towards-- Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Alexandrovicz came closer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, 'This is a young lady who tried to get a job here.' And he looked at me and smiled.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, 'Wait a minute,' and asked me to the office, in the office.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, 'Yes,' and that my wish always was to work here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow, he was impressed, and I got the job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we did have a daily contact with the bosses, because they work-- they were almost at all the time in the office-- in the business, yeah.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it must be two years, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was '38.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] '38, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, when the war started and the bosses did run away-- actually, I must remember-- there were also people employed, not Jewish, actually.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the office, they was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
